&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code&gt;config.generators do |g|
   g.test_framework  nil
end&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then subsequent generators won't generate any test files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
