application.rb will contain&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;config.generators do |g|&lt;br&gt;
g.test_framework nil end&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which will then mean that any future generators will not
generate any test files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
